<div class="text-block row">
	<div class="large-8 columns large-offset-2">
		<h4>The Problem</h4>
		<p>In 2011, Jawbone had already released the JAMBOX, and was working on the next generation speaker – the BIG JAMBOX. Not only was it going to have superior sound quality, it was also going to come with additional media controls, like playing/pausing music, and skipping to previous/next tracks.</p>
		<p>I was tasked with helping determine how the BIG JAMBOX's buttons could be arranged to provide the most intuitive user experience by creating and conducting internal usability studies.</p>
	</div>
</div>

