		<h4>Methodology</h4>
		<p>Prior to conducting the user testing, I came up with the methodology for the test, including the types of users I wanted to interview, as well as the script with questions that would ultimately inform the design of the buttons. I interviewed ten users, all of whom were familiar with the regular version of the JAMBOX.</p>
